124
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,150
Let me take care of you.

125
00:06:21,590 --> 00:06:23,550
A man shouldn't be so spineless.

126
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:26,470
You took the first step

127
00:06:27,030 --> 00:06:28,640
and you decided to be

128
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:29,800
someone extraordinary.

129
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:30,990
Then you should

130
00:06:30,990 --> 00:06:32,310
use your own power

131
00:06:32,710 --> 00:06:33,800
to face the world.

132
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:35,590
Hiding in my shadow

133
00:06:35,990 --> 00:06:37,470
won't make you grow.

134
00:06:38,150 --> 00:06:40,120
But I want to train

135
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,030
and learn from you.

136
00:06:42,550 --> 00:06:44,400
Master will bring you

137
00:06:45,030 --> 00:06:46,200
