150
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:22,520
Dad.

151
00:07:23,350 --> 00:07:25,160
Where are you going?

152
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:28,670
You have your own path

153
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:30,480
and I

154
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,200
have to face my fate.

155
00:07:37,910 --> 00:07:38,430
Dad.

156
00:07:38,790 --> 00:07:39,430
Dad.

157
00:08:01,990 --> 00:08:02,750
