165
00:08:26,990 --> 00:08:27,600
It's fine.

166
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:29,400
Once I'm strong enough,

167
00:08:29,910 --> 00:08:30,960
I'll ask him myself.

168
00:08:32,350 --> 00:08:33,040
Master,

169
00:08:33,790 --> 00:08:35,230
I want to attend the best school

170
00:08:35,670 --> 00:08:36,870
and be the strongest Soul Master.

171
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:38,750
I'll be with you.

172
00:08:40,110 --> 00:08:41,720
