is looking for you.

173
00:08:42,430 --> 00:08:44,310
Most schools are no-go.

174
00:08:44,990 --> 00:08:46,280
Any alternatives?

175
00:08:46,910 --> 00:08:48,400
Martial Soul Hall or the seven clans.

176
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,960
Comparing both,

177
00:08:50,110 --> 00:08:51,310
Martial Soul Hall

178
00:08:51,910 --> 00:08:53,480
