No need to persuade me.

186
00:09:09,110 --> 00:09:09,870
You're wasting your time.

187
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:14,520
Master.

188
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,910
What about the seven clans?

189
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:19,350
Other than normal schools
and Martial Soul Hall,

190
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:20,840
in Douluo Continent, there are

191
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,230
seven renowned Soul Master tribes.

192
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,960
These seven tribes stick to themselves

193
00:09:25,430 --> 00:09:26,600
