but when you're done,

197
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,160
you have to work for the clan.

198
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:32,350
That's only fair.

199
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,640
For how long?

200
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:35,040
The rest of your life.

201
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:38,280
And outsiders

202
00:09:38,430 --> 00:09:39,990
