by the in-house Soul Masters.

203
00:09:40,990 --> 00:09:42,550
So outsiders like us

204
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:43,910
can never succeed then?

205
00:09:45,230 --> 00:09:46,280
Who do these clans

206
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,480
treat outsiders so?

207
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:48,840
Every clan

208
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,960
wants to control their own Soul Masters.

209
00:09:51,670 --> 00:09:52,750
This is inevitable.

210
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,400
Any other option?

211
00:09:59,040 --> 00:09:59,670
If you don't want

212
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:00,960
to be bound to any party,

213
00:10:01,790 --> 00:10:03,040
there's one option:

214
00:10:05,310 --> 00:10:06,080
Devil's School.

215
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,110
Stop!

216
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:15,840
