217
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,480
No?

218
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:18,910
Of course not.

219
00:10:20,350 --> 00:10:21,670
Devil's School is a nickname.

220
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,280
Every student there

221
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:24,670
is powerful beyond comprehension,

222
00:10:25,350 --> 00:10:26,640
