228
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,750
Shi Lan Ke.

229
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:39,520
Devil's School sounds better.

230
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,080
Regardless of your status

231
00:10:41,110 --> 00:10:41,790
