233
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,350
Where is this Shi Lan Ke School?

234
00:10:46,550 --> 00:10:47,400
In Suo Tuo City.

235
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,990
Suo Tuo City belongs to Tian Dou Empire.

236
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:51,910
To commemorate

237
00:10:51,910 --> 00:10:53,160
an old but beautiful love story,

238
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:54,960
the two cities in this empire

239
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,200
are named after

240
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,200
Suo Tuo and Fei Ren.

241
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:00,040
As time goes by,

242
00:11:01,430 --> 00:11:02,960
Fei Ren City is in ruin

243
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:06,040
while Suo Tuo City continues to prosper.

244
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:09,230
All right. That's all.

245
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:10,720
It's quite far from here.

246
00:11:10,990 --> 00:11:11,990
Rest early.

247
00:11:12,430 --> 00:11:13,600
We'll move at sunrise.

248
00:11:14,110 --> 00:11:14,640
Okay!

249
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:16,280
Wait,

250
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:18,960
